name: dunder_quota_attainment
xsql: select      total_sales,      employee_quota,      Round((total_sales / employee_quota) * 100, 2) || '%' as attainment_percentage from (     select          sum(o.amount) as total_sales,          e.quota_amount as employee_quota     from          $framework.dunderorders o     join          $framework.dunderemployees e on o.employee_id = e.employee_id     where          o.employee_id = :v_employee_id     group by          e.quota_amount );
